This dataset is from the NAACL 2024 paper "Improving Adversarial Data Collection by Supporting Annotators: Lessons from GAHD, a German Hate Speech Dataset" by Janis Goldzycher, Paul Röttger, and Gerold Schneider.

The dataset is available under the Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0) license.

When using GAHD, please cite the following paper:

@misc{goldzycher2024improving,
      title={Improving Adversarial Data Collection by Supporting Annotators: Lessons from GAHD, a German Hate Speech Dataset}, 
      author={Janis Goldzycher and Paul Röttger and Gerold Schneider},
      year={2024},
      eprint={2403.19559},
      archivePrefix={arXiv},
      primaryClass={cs.CL}
}
